---
import { siteBase } from "../lib/base";
import Handbook from "../layouts/Handbook.astro";
const base = siteBase();
---
<Handbook title="更多" current="guides">
  <p class="eyebrow">導覽</p>
  <h1 class="page-title">教材已移到這裡</h1>
  <span class="status status-provisional">目前暫定</span>
  <p>交通、食物、出發前、購物等高價值教材改由底部「教材」與首頁「先找這些」進入，不再藏在模糊的更多選單。</p>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a class="btn primary" href={`${base}guides/`}>打開教材目錄</a>
    <a class="btn" href={`${base}decisions/`}>一起決定</a>
    <a class="btn" href={`${base}emergency/`}>緊急</a>
  </div>
</Handbook>
